cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about language modelling and analyzing the effectiveness of different models.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper compares two different types of models and analyzes their performance.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep neural networks and their application in language modelling.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper focuses on the Long Short-Term Memory Model, which is a type of recurrent neural network.
- cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with language modelling, which can be applied to speech recognition and synthesis.
